<description>

Fixed Deposit and Recurring Deposit accounts are created from the Client Detail page. The FD Account creation form contains Fixed Deposit Product dropdown, Deposit Amount, Deposit Period (numeric and unit — Days, Months, Years), and Maturity Instructions (Transfer to Savings, Re-Invest, or Re-Invest Principal and Transfer Interest). The FD Account Detail page shows deposit amount, maturity date, maturity amount, interest rate, and status with action buttons for Approve, Activate, Premature Close, and Close on Maturity. The RD Account creation form contains Recurring Deposit Product dropdown, Mandatory Deposit Amount per installment, Deposit Period, Deposit Frequency (Daily, Weekly, Monthly, Quarterly, Yearly), and Expected First Deposit On date. The RD Account Detail page shows the deposit schedule, total deposits made, maturity details, interest rate, and status with action buttons for Approve, Activate, Deposit, Premature Close, and Close on Maturity. Both FD and RD detail pages include tabs for Summary, Transactions, and Charges. Interest rates are determined by the Interest Rate Chart configured on the product, with tiered rates based on deposit amount and term length.

---


</description>

<workflows>
WF-001 | Create Fixed Deposit account | actor: <role> | branch: none | terminal: Create Fixed Deposit | on_success: Fixed Deposit account created; detail page shows deposit amount, maturity date, maturity amount, interest rate, and status.
WF-002 | Create Recurring Deposit account | actor: <role> | branch: none | terminal: Create Recurring Deposit | on_success: Recurring Deposit account created; detail page shows deposit schedule, total deposits made, maturity details, and interest rate.
WF-003 | Approve Fixed Deposit account | actor: <role> | branch: none | terminal: Approve | on_success: Fixed Deposit account approved; status updated to Approved.
WF-004 | Activate Fixed Deposit account | actor: <role> | branch: none | terminal: Activate | on_success: Fixed Deposit account activated; status updated to Active.
WF-005 | Prematurely close Fixed Deposit account | actor: <role> | branch: none | terminal: Premature Close | on_success: Fixed Deposit account prematurely closed; balances settled per product rules.
WF-006 | Close Fixed Deposit account on maturity | actor: <role> | branch: none | terminal: Close on Maturity | on_success: Fixed Deposit account closed on maturity; maturity amount handled per Maturity Instructions.
WF-007 | Approve Recurring Deposit account | actor: <role> | branch: none | terminal: Approve | on_success: Recurring Deposit account approved; status updated to Approved.
WF-008 | Activate Recurring Deposit account | actor: <role> | branch: none | terminal: Activate | on_success: Recurring Deposit account activated; status updated to Active.
WF-009 | Record Deposit to Recurring Deposit account | actor: <role> | branch: none | terminal: Deposit | on_success: Deposit recorded against Recurring Deposit account; deposit schedule and total deposits updated.
WF-010 | Prematurely close Recurring Deposit account | actor: <role> | branch: none | terminal: Premature Close | on_success: Recurring Deposit account prematurely closed; balances settled per product rules.
WF-011 | Close Recurring Deposit account on maturity | actor: <role> | branch: none | terminal: Close on Maturity | on_success: Recurring Deposit account closed on maturity; maturity amount handled per product and schedule.
</workflows>

